 * Scala port for SGE
 *
 * Quick procedural IBL environment generation.
 * Should be closed when no longer used.
 *
 * IBL generated by this class are accurate, some fast approximation are performed to provide
 * a quick way to setup an IBL environment. For accurate IBL, see:
 * https://learnopengl.com/PBR/IBL/Specular-IBL
 * and
 * https://learnopengl.com/PBR/IBL/Diffuse-irradiance
 * and related tools to generate them from HDRIs.
 *
 * Migration notes:
 *   Convention: uses (using Sge) context parameter
 *   Convention: rect() → rectangle(), dispose() → close(), getSide() → side (Nullable)
 *   Convention: typed GL enums (EnableCap, BlendFactor, ClearMask)
 *   Idiom: split packages
 *   Audited: 2026-04-18
 *
 * Covenant: full-port
